OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FTaylor Swift has applied to trademark
OL,7,Fher voice and image, amid growing
OL,8,Fconcerns of content generated by
OL,9,Fartificial intelligence.
OL,11,FThe 36-year-old, known for the hit
OL,12,Fsongs Love Story and Shake It Off,
OL,13,Fsubmitted three applications in the US
OL,14,Fon Friday to trademark her voice and
OL,15,Flikeness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
