FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FThe applications included an image of
OL,7,Fherself from the Eras tour, along with
OL,8,Ftwo audio clips where she introduced
OL,9,Fherself while promoting her most
OL,10,Frecent studio album, The Life Of A
OL,11,FShowgirl.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
