PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FThe image submitted was used to
OL,7,Fpromote Swift's Disney+ docuseries The
OL,8,FEnd Of An Era, and was described in
OL,9,Fthe court filing as: "Taylor Swift
OL,10,Fholding a pink guitar, with a black
OL,11,Fstrap and wearing a multi-colored
OL,12,Firidescent bodysuit with silver boots.
OL,13,FShe is standing on a pink stage in
OL,14,Ffront of a multi-coloured microphone
OL,15,Fwith purple lights in the background."
OL,26,@qD@VOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
