PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FOne of the audio clips featured the
OL,7,Fstar saying: "Hey, it's Taylor Swift"
OL,8,Fwhile in the second she says: "Hey,
OL,9,Fit's Taylor. My brand new album The
OL,10,FLife Of A Showgirl is out on October 3
OL,11,Fand you can click to pre-save it so
OL,12,Fyou can listen to it on Spotify."
OL,14,FInterstellar actor Matthew McConaughey
OL,15,Frecently told the Wall Street Journal
OL,16,Fhe had trademarked his voice and image
OL,17,Fto protect himself from any
OL,18,Funauthorised use by AI apps.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@eO]pD@_OUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
