PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FIt is unlikely that cases will be
OL,7,Fbrought against people making AI-
OL,8,Fgenerated clips of Swift for fun at
OL,9,Fhome, but as AI advances, there is a
OL,10,Fgrowing chance that people will
OL,11,Fattempt to start commercial
OL,12,Fenterprises with AI bots trained to
OL,13,Fappear like her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
