PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FAlthough protecting sound is not a new
OL,7,Fconcept, according to trademark
OL,8,Fattorney Josh Gerben ` who first
OL,9,Fhighlighted the details of the
OL,10,Fapplications on his site GerbenLaw `
OL,11,Finvolving spoken voice through audio
OL,12,Fclips has not been tested in US courts
OL,13,Fbefore.
OL,15,FMr Gerben added that the applications
OL,16,Fcould provide Swift with an
OL,17,F"additional layer of protection".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
