PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FHe said: "By registering specific
OL,7,Fphrases tied to her voice, Swift could
OL,8,Fpotentially challenge not only
OL,9,Fidentical reproductions, but also
OL,10,Fimitations that are "confusingly
OL,11,Fsimilar," a key standard in trademark
OL,12,Flaw.
OL,14,F"The image-based filing serves a
OL,15,Fsimilar purpose: by protecting a
OL,16,Fdistinctive visual, down to Swift's
OL,17,Fcommonly worn jumpsuit and pose,
OL,18,FSwift's team may gain additional
OL,19,Fgrounds to pursue claims against
OL,20,Fmanipulated or AI-generated images
OL,21,Fthat evoke her likeness."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@UOUsD@IO]vD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
