PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,FHe said that historically in the US,
OL,7,Fartists would either use copyright law
OL,8,Fto protect their music or right of
OL,9,Fpublicity laws to protect their
OL,10,Flikeness or image, however
OL,11,Ftrademarking Swift's sound and image
OL,12,Fcould increase her protection.
OL,14,FHe continued: "AI has broken that
OL,15,Fmodel. Now, anyone can spin up a
OL,16,Fversion of an artist's voice, have it
OL,17,Fsay anything, attach it to anything
OL,18,Fand distribute it at scale.
OL,26,@vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
