FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777370785
OL,3,CTaylor Swift applies to trademark her
OL,4,Cvoice over growing AI threat
OL,6,F"That's where trademarks come in.
OL,7,FTrademark law doesn't just stop
OL,8,Fidentical uses (like copyright law):
OL,9,Fit stops anything that is confusingly
OL,10,Fsimilar to the registered trademark.
OL,11,FThat's a much broader right and more
OL,12,Fpowerful tool in an AI world."
